Show Description

From the Infowars web site :: On this jam-packed Tuesday, September 3 edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex continues to explain the unprecedented move by the White House to back off on an immediate war in Syria following intense pressure from alternative media. The war drums continue beating though as the U.S. and Israel have recently carried out a joint missile test in the Mediterranean. Russia has sent scout ships to the Syrian coast in response. 

NSA whistleblower Wayne Madsen joins the show to discuss these recent developments in Syria. Hollywood actors Roddy Piper and Sean Stone also join the show to talk about the 25th anniversary of the iconic film They Live as well as the situation in Syria.
